'''Uruguayans in the Netherlands''' are people born in [[Uruguay]] who live in the [[Netherlands]], or Dutch-born people of Uruguayan descent. <!-- As of 2016, there were over 100 Uruguayans living in Dutch territory -->.

During the [[civic-military dictatorship of Uruguay]] (1973-1985) several Uruguayans went into exile in the Netherlands.

